    2026-05-19T14:40:38Z)

(Decision
    "Rename the repository-ledger contract and implementation away from redundant `Repository*` prefixes where the repository-ledger crate, channel, or component already supplies that context. Apply the naming rule immediately, not just as future guidance."
    "rename everything"
